., (2003) The New Swiss Glacier Inventory 2000: Application of Remote Sensing and GIS, , PhD thesis, University of Zürich; Paul, F., Kaar, A., Maisch, M., Kellenberger, T., Haeberli, W., The new remote-sensing-derived Swiss glacier inventory: I. Methods (2002) Annals of Glaciology, 34, pp. 355-361. , Papers from the Fourth International Symposium on Remote Sensing in Glaciology held in Colleg Park, Maryland, USA, 3-8 June 2001; Paul, F., Huggel, C., Kaab, A., Combining satellite multispectral image data and a digital elevation model for mapping debris-covered glaciers (2004) Remote Sensing of Environment, 89 (4), pp. 510-518. , DOI 10.1016/j.rse.2003.11.007; Phillips, W.M., Sloan, V.F., Shroder Jr., J.F., Sharma, P., Clarke, M.L., Rendell, H.M., Asynchronous glaciation at nanga parbat, nortwestern himalaya mountains, Pakistan (2000) Geology, 28 (5), pp. 431-434; Pillewizer, W., Der Rakhiot-Gletscher am Nanga Parbat im Jahre 1954. Z (1956) Gletscherkd. Glazialgeol, 3 (2), pp. 181-194; Richards, B.W., Owen, L.A., Rhodes, E.J., Timing of late quaternary glaciations in the himalayas of northern Pakistan (2000) Journal of Quaternary Science, 15 (3), pp. 283-297. , DOI 10.1002/(SICI)1099-1417(200003)15:3<283::AID-JQS525>3.0.CO;2-X; Shroder, J.F., Bishop, M.P., Copland, L., Sloan, V.F., Debris-covered glaciers and rock glaciers in the Nanga Parbat Himalaya, Pakistan (2000) Geografiska Annaler, Series A: Physical Geography, 82 (1), pp. 17-31; Shukla, A., Gupta, R.P., Arora, M.K., Estimation of debris cover and its temporal variation using optical satellite sensor data: A case study in Chenab basin, Himalayas (2009) J. Glaciol., 55 (191), pp. 444-452; Smiraglia, C., Mayer, C., Mihalcea, C., Diolaiuti, G., Belò, M., Vassena, G., Ongoing variations of himalayan and karakoram glaciers as witnesses of global changes: Recent studies on selected glaciers (2007) Mountain Witnesses of Global Changes., pp. 235-248. , Baudo, R., G. Tartari and E. Vuillermoz, eds. Amsterdam, Elsevier; 